
📌 Overview

This project presents an interactive Power BI dashboard designed to analyze e-commerce product returns and uncover key patterns affecting business performance. It helps stakeholders understand return behavior and make data-driven decisions.

🚀 Key Metrics
Net Sales: 2.33M
Net Orders: 10K
Net Returns: 297
Return Rate: 2.91%
Net Profit: 292.30K
📈 Features
Return Rate Analysis across product categories
Sales vs Return Insights
Top Sub-category Returns Identification
Monthly Return Trends Visualization
Geographic Analysis (Region & Country)
Customer Segment Insights
Shipping Mode Impact on Returns
🧠 Insights
Technology and Furniture categories show varying return patterns
Certain shipping modes contribute more to returns
Regional trends highlight areas with higher return rates
Consumer segment drives the majority of returns
🛠 Tools Used
Power BI Desktop
Data Visualization Techniques
Business Intelligence Analysis
📂 Project File
E-Commerce Returns Analysis Dashboard.pbix
🎯 Purpose

The goal of this dashboard is to help businesses:

Reduce return rates
Improve logistics efficiency
Enhance customer satisfaction
Optimize product quality
